e common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert Marche was born in 1475, in Sherford, Devon, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Marche."},"et":{"1475–":"1475–Surnud","1475–Female":"1475–Surnud","1500–Male":"1500–Surnud","1475–Male":"1475–Surnud","1500":"1500","1475":"1475","Sherford, Devon, England, UK":"Sherford, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1475–":"1475–Kuollut","1475–Female":"1475–Kuollut","1500–Male":"1500–Kuollut","1475–Male":"1475–Kuollut","1500":"1500","1475":"1475","Sherford, Devon, England, UK":"Sherford, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1475–":"1475–Décédé","1475–Female":"1475–Décédée","1500–Male":"1500–Décédé","1475–Male":"1475–Décédé","1500":"1500","1475":"1475","Sherford, Devon, England, UK":"Sherford, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Robert Marche est né en 1475, à Sherford, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Marche."},"de":{"1475–":"1475–Verstorben","1475–Female":"1475–Verstorben","1500–Male":"1500–Verstorben","1475–Male":"1475–Verstorben","1500":"1500","1475":"1475","Sherford, Devon, England, UK":"Sherford, Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Robert Marche wurde 1475 in Sherford, Devon, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mit Marche mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1475–":"1475–Desede","1475–Female":"1475–Desede","1500–Male":"1500–Desede","1475–Male":"1475–Desede","1500":"1500","1475":"1475","Sherford, Devon, England, UK":"Sherford, Devon, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1475–":"1475–elhunyt","1475–Female":"1475–elhunyt","1500–Male":"1500–elhunyt","1475–Male":"1475–elhunyt","1500":"1500","1475":"1475","Sherford, Devon, England, UK":"Sherford, Devon, Anglia, United Kingdom"},"id":{"1475–":"1475–Telah Meninggal","1475–Female":"1475–Telah Meninggal","1500–Male":"1500–Telah Meninggal","1475–Male":"1475–Telah Meninggal","1500":"1500","1475":"1475","Sherford, Devon, England, UK"